OL,3,CBangs heard and arrest made after
OL,4,Carmed police swarm retail park
OL,6,FArmed police have swarmed a retail
OL,7,Fpark in Sussex after receiving reports
OL,8,Fa man was walking with a bladed weapon.
OL,10,FMultiple response officers attended
OL,11,Fthe scene at Ravenside Retail and
OL,12,FLeisure Park in De La Warr Road,
OL,13,FBexhill after the alarm was raised
OL,14,Fabout the suspect on nearby Third
OL,15,FAvenue.
OL,17,FThe incident happened around 12:40pm
OL,18,Fon Saturday and eyewitness videos from
OL,19,Fthe incident captured loud bangs as
OL,20,Fpolice carried out their operation.
