OL,3,CBangs heard and arrest made after
OL,4,Carmed police swarm retail park
OL,6,FA 46-year-old man was arrested on
OL,7,Fsuspicion of attempted grievous bodily
OL,8,Fharm, possession of a bladed article
OL,9,Fin a public place, affray, and
OL,10,Fcriminal damage.
OL,12,FHe has been taken to hospital to be
OL,13,Ftreated for medical checks and no
OL,14,Fmembers of the public were harmed.
OL,16,FSuperintendent Jonathan Hartley said:
OL,17,F"We understand the concern this
OL,18,Fincident will have caused, and I'd
OL,19,Flike to reassure the community that
OL,20,Fthere is no wider threat to the public.
OL,26,@yD@AOU
