OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1779095182
OL,3,CBangs heard and arrest made after
OL,4,Carmed police swarm retail park
OL,6,F"Our priority is safety, and the
OL,7,Fdeployment of distraction tactics
OL,8,Fenabled officers to swiftly detain the
OL,9,Fman and ensure public safety.
OL,11,F"We recognise the ongoing disruption
OL,12,Fthis incident may cause as officers
OL,13,Fremain at the scene conducting initial
OL,14,Fenquiries, and I'd like to thank the
OL,15,Fcommunity for their patience and
OL,16,Funderstanding during this time."
